properties.description: Posted by Jason Controversial artist Parker Burnmill sets up his guerrilla art gallery right here (or nearby) on the last thursday of each month. Adorning the trappings of the extrovert with the kitschy reverie of the loner artiste, Burnmill has created an irresistible blend of cultural experimentation. Go visit him to gawk, to collect, or to engage him in debate about almost anything.

properties.name: Old man gettin jiggy on the plane
properties.description: Posted by Jason off 880, Oakland, CAOn our descent an older gentleman dropped a quarter from his pocket onto the aisle. He just kept looking between his legs and I guess I could have pointed out where it was but he seemed kinds skittish. As we got closer to the landing strip he decides to just get up and look for it. We are seriously like about to land and this guy is cluelessly tottering around in the aisle. I\'m ready to catch him if it comes to that. The attendant swoops in with his kind of gentle martial arts move to get him seated and buckled in just before the tires touch down.
